  "notes": "* <span class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Spell shield\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\"><a title=\"Spell shield\" href=\"/wiki/Spell_shield\"><img alt=\"Spell Shield\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-image-key=\"Sivir_Spell_Shield.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a0/Sivir_Spell_Shield.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170818194532\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" class=\"lazyload\" width=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Sivir Spell Shield.png\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Spell_shield\" title=\"Spell shield\">Spell shield</a></span> will block only a single instance of damage - either the thrust or the slash.\n<ul><li>The first strike will occur immediately and the second will occur after the cast time completes.</li>\n<li>This ability will cast from wherever the caster is at the start of the cast time.\n<ul><li>The first strike will occur from wherever <b>Xin Zhao</b> is at the start of the cast time.</li></ul></li>\n<li>This ability will cast from wherever the caster is at the end of the cast time.\n<ul><li>The second strike will occur from wherever <b>Xin Zhao</b> is at the end of the cast time.</li></ul></li>\n<li>The first strike's hitbox includes a <span style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Er\" class=\"glossary\"><a href=\"/wiki/Range\" title=\"Range\"><img width=\"20\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" height=\"20\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Range model\" class=\"lazyload\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-key=\"Range_model.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-image-name=\"Range model.png\"></a></span> 275 radius 160° cone in front of <b>Xin Zhao</b> and an additional <span class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Cr\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\"><a title=\"Range\" href=\"/wiki/Range\"><img data-image-key=\"Range_center.png\" width=\"20\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" alt=\"Range center\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Range_center.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134211\" data-relevant=\"1\" class=\"lazyload\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Range center.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></span> 125 radius around him.</li>\n<li>The second strike's hitbox includes the same <span class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Cr\"><a href=\"/wiki/Range\" title=\"Range\"><img data-image-name=\"Range center.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-key=\"Range_center.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Range_center.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134211\" class=\"lazyload\" alt=\"Range center\" width=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"20\"></a></span> 125 radius around <b>Xin Zhao</b>, a missile with <span data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Cr\" class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Range\" title=\"Range\"><img alt=\"Range center\" class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Range_center.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134211\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Range center.png\" data-image-key=\"Range_center.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-relevant=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\"></a></span> 1000 range and <span data-tip=\"Er\" class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\"><a href=\"/wiki/Range\" title=\"Range\"><img data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216\" width=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" alt=\"Range model\" data-image-key=\"Range_model.png\" class=\"lazyload\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Range model.png\" data-relevant=\"1\"></a></span> 80 total width, and a <span class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Er\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\"><a href=\"/wiki/Range\" title=\"Range\"><img alt=\"Range model\" height=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-image-key=\"Range_model.png\" data-image-name=\"Range model.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216\"></a></span> -60 radius area check upon the end of the missile.\n<ul><li>The 125 radius check does not hit <a href=\"/wiki/Champion_summoned_units\" title=\"Champion summoned units\">champion summoned units</a>.<sup><span style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;\" title=\"This may not be intended.\" class=\"basic-tooltip\">(bug)</span></sup></li></ul></li>\n<li>Because <i>Wind Becomes Lightning</i> uses an older type of 'healing based on life steal' and not <i><span class=\"glossary\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Applies life steal\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Life_steal\" title=\"Life steal\">applies life steal</a></span></i>, <span data-param=\"\" data-game=\"lol\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" class=\"inline-image label-after item-icon\" data-item=\"Spirit Visage\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\"><a href=\"/wiki/Spirit_Visage\" title=\"Spirit Visage\"><img data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/6f/Spirit_Visage_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201118210426\" decoding=\"async\" data-image-name=\"Spirit Visage item.png\" width=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-key=\"Spirit_Visage_item.png\" alt=\"Spirit Visage\" data-relevant=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Spirit_Visage\" title=\"Spirit Visage\">Spirit Visage</a></span></span> will amplify the life gain twice (+25% life steal and +25% healing), for a total of +56.<small>25</small>%.</li></ul>",
